ble | resolved-not-applicable | target-search, sdk-declaration, cangjie-callable | not-needed |\n148: \n149: ## Full Report Pointers\n150: \n151: - `phaseTaskChecklist`: `D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\phase-task-checklist.md`\n152: - `planSeed`: `D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\plan-seed.md`\n153: - `planValidationReport`: `D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\plan-validation-report.md`\n154: - `phaseGroupVerdicts`: `D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\phase-group-verdicts.md`\n155: - `phaseCoverageGate`: `D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\phase-coverage-gate-report.md`\n156: - `translationQualitySummary`: `D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\translation-quality-summary.md`\n157: - `sourceCoverageMatrix`: `D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\source-coverage-matrix.json`\n158: - `platformCapabilityCheck`: `D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\platform-capability-check.json`\n159: - `targetStructureReport`: `D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\target-structure-report.md`\n\n(End of file - total 159 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Agent Input Brief - phase-05-detail-cart / coverage-repair\n\nThis brief is a narrow planning input compiled from current workflow reports. It is not an authority file.\nStart here, then open only the referenced source paths, target endpoints, capabilities, or reports needed for the task.\n\n## Boundaries\n\n- Source project: `D:\\Kotlin2Cangjie\\Foodike`\n- Target project: `D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\Foodike-Harmony`\n- Translation inputs: `D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs`\n- Do not read sibling old translations unless the user explicitly asks for comparison.\n- Edit only target project files and agent-maintained authority files required by the current session.\n\n## Freshness\n\n| artifact | exists | generatedAt | phase | error |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| phaseTaskChecklist | yes | 2026-06-28T11:28:25+00:00 | phase-05-detail-cart