/notes explanation\",\n49:         \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-detai-7936c7449c-002-runtime-permission-request-permission-re: not-applicable has source/notes explanation\",\n50:         \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-domain-model-menui-7b27ec2c61-001-navigation-surface-menu-drawer-toolbar-o: not-applicable has source/notes explanation\",\n51:         \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-domain-model-menui-9a25063300-002-runtime-permission-request-permission-re: not-applicable has source/notes explanation\",\n52:         \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-cart-57b6b92fe8-001-navigation-surface-menu-drawer-toolbar-o: not-applicable has source/notes explanation\",\n53:         \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-cart-73f81907e8-002-runtime-permission-request-permission-re: not-applicable has source/notes explanation\",\n54:         \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-domain-model-carti-beeee34863-001-navigation-surface-menu-drawer-toolbar-o: not-applicable has source/notes explanation\"\n55:       ],\n56:       \"contractDebt\": [],\n57:       \"sourcePaths\": [\n58:         \"app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/details/RestaurantDetail.kt\",\n59:         \"app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/cart/Cart.kt\",\n60:         \"app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/details/RestaurantDetailViewModel.kt\",\n61:         \"app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/cart/CartViewModel.kt\",\n62:         \"app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/details/DetailScreenState.kt\",\n63:         \"app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/domain/model/MenuItem.kt\",\n64:         \"app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/cart/CartState.kt\",\n65:         \"app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/domain/model/CartItem.kt\"\n66:       ],\n67:       \"featureIds\": [\n68:         \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-detai-ee3681ccdd-002-intent-uri-bundle-deeplink-or-cross-scre\",\n69:         \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-detai-958b17f285-005-observable-state-viewmodel-flow-livedata\",\n70:         \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-cart-9969033ff2-004-screen-lifecycle-entry-point-initializat\",\n71:         \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-cart-f1f520ab22-005-observable-state-viewmodel-flow-livedata\",\n72:         \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-detai-b9908eedc8-002-runtime-permission-request-permission-re\",\n73:         \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-detai-fe3552443b-003-screen-lifecycle-entry-point-initializat\",\n74:         \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-detai-4fdb060ca4-004-observable-state-viewmodel-flow-livedata\",\n75:         \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-cart-33250392eb-001-runtime-permission-request-permission-re\",\n76:         \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-cart-3db8c1ab5c-002-screen-lifecycle-entry-point-initializat\",\n77:         \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-cart-9cef776f25-003-observable-state-viewmodel-flow-livedata\",\n78:         \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-detai-76b993fa5a-001-navigation-surface-menu-drawer-toolbar-o\",\n79:         \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-detai-7936c7449c-002-runtime-permission-request-permission-re\",\n80:         \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-domain-model-menui-7b27ec2c61-001-navigation-surface-menu-drawer-toolbar-o\",\n81:         \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-domain-model-menui-9a25063300-002-runtime-permission-request-permission-re\",\n82:         \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-cart-57b6b92fe8-001-navigation-surface-menu-drawer-toolbar-o\",\n83:         \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-cart-73f81907e8-002-runtime-permission-request-permission-re\",\n84:         \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-domain-model-carti-beeee34863-001-navigation-surface-menu-drawer-toolbar-o\"\n85:       ],\n86:       \"resourceInputs\": [],\n87:       \"platformCapabilityIds\": [],\n88:       \"expectedTargetDomains\": [\n89:         \"ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj\",\n90:         \"ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/route_registry.cj\",\n91:         \"ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/detail/detail_store.cj\",\n92:         \"ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/detail/detail_page.cj\",\n93:         \"ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/cart/cart_store.cj\",\n94:         \"ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/cart/cart_page.cj\",\n95:         \"ohos_app_cangjie_entry/data/session/session_repository.cj\",\n96:         \"ohos_app_cangjie_entry/domain/discovery_models.cj\"\n97:       ],\n98:       \"requiredBehaviors\": [\n99:         \"`FoodikeBootstrap.goToRestaurantDetail()` navigates to the fixed `restaurant_details` route after the home/history stores save the selected restaurant in shared session state, and `detailStore.selectedRestaurant()` / `loadDetailState(...)` rebuild the detai...\",\n100:         \"`FoodikeBootstrap.detailState()` reloads `DetailPageState` from `detailStore.loadDetailState(...)` each render, while `buildDetailRoute` mutates expansion flags and quantity revisions so `renderDetailRoute` re-renders section visibility and cart action stat...\",\n101:         \"`FoodikeBootstrap.buildCartRoute` reloads `CartPageState` when the cart route renders, keeps note/coupon route state alive while the route is active, and preserves the source's single active-screen composition pattern without adding extra resume/pause hooks.\",\n102:         \"`buildCartRoute` reloads `CartPageState` from `CartStore`, `renderCartRoute` derives visible items through `cartStore.visibleItems(...)`, and quantity changes propagate through the shared session repository so cart contents and totals refresh immediately ac...\",\n103:         \"`detailStore.loadDetailState(...)` and `FoodikeBootstrap.buildDetailRoute` preserve the same permission-free state loading and reducer behavior in the HarmonyOS target.\",\n104:         \"`FoodikeBootstrap.goToRestaurantDetail()` resets section flags and liked state before navigation, and `detailState()` calls `detailStore.loadDetailState(...)` each time the detail route renders so the translated detail screen reloads selected restaurant and...\",\n105:         \"`detailStore.loadDetailState(...)` rebuilds `DetailPageState` from shared session data and current expansion flags, while quantity changes and like toggles update shared session state so subsequent detail/cart renders observe the new values immediately.\",\n106:         \"The translated cart store and route bootstrap preserve this permission-free state-loading flow.\",\n107:         \"`CartStore.loadCartState()` is invoked each time `FoodikeBootstrap.buildCartRoute` renders the cart route, preserving source entrypoint loading semantics without adding extra lifecycle phases.\",\n108:         \"`CartStore.loadCartState()` reads the shared session cart snapshot, and `FoodikeBootstrap.buildCartRoute` rerenders after cart mutations so translated cart state stays synchronized with session-backed quantity changes.\",\n109:         \"`DetailPageState` remains a data-only state model in the HarmonyOS target, with all detail route and toolbar commands owned by `renderDetailRoute` and `FoodikeBootstrap.buildDetailRoute` instead of the state struct.\",\n110:         \"`DetailPageState` remains a data-only state model in the HarmonyOS target with no permission-handling path.\",\n111:         \"The HarmonyOS target keeps `MenuItem` as pure menu data through `MenuItemData`, then consumes that data from detail/cart stores and pages without placing navigation behavior inside the domain model layer.\",\n112:         \"The HarmonyOS target keeps the menu item model as data-only through `MenuItemData` and related detail/cart 